73 Emergency clause. In view of the emergency cited in the preamble, this legislation
84 takes effect when approved.
9 SUMMARY
1100 This bill establishes Maine's Care Force, a program within the Department of Health
1111 and Human Services to place individuals trained as essential support workers by the
1122 department in private homes, facilities and community-based settings. It provides for
1133 ongoing annual appropriations of $32,000,000 to support the program.
